## 📊 Real-Time Dashboard

A custom web dashboard was developed to visualize telemetry from all ECUs in real time.

The dashboard provides:

- Vehicle Speed
- MPU6050 Accelerometer
- MPU6050 Gyroscope
- Temperature
- Humidity
- DS18B20 Temperature
- Motion Snapshot
- Live CAN Stream
- Historical Graphs
- Sensor Health Monitoring

